data.description: Welcome to this charming, Richmond Heights colonial. This lovely and well maintained home offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The corner lot offers a ton of yard space to enjoy with your family! A lovely blend of indoor/outdoor living is supplemented by the patio area surrounded by privacy fencing. The partially finished basement offers the perfect blend of additional living space to use at your discretion and storage space. This home has many updates and has been extremely well cared for.
